---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="What is WISMO, and Why Should You Care About It? - parcelLab" description="An overview of WISMO (Where Is My Order?) inquiries in e-commerce, their impact on customer service, and strategies to reduce them.">
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
      <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>Back to blog</a>
      <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Research</span>
      <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">What is WISMO, and Why Should You Care About It?</h1>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
        <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab</strong></span><span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
        <time datetime="2021-04-11">April 11, 2021</time><span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span><span>4 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div></div></section>
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">WISMO stands for "Where is my order?" and serves as an umbrella term for inbound customer inquiries regarding shipment status. Though seemingly minor, unmanaged WISMO requests create significant operational challenges.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">The Challenges</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Global brands face substantial obstacles when tracking orders post-shipment. Carrier systems employ proprietary data tagging that proves difficult for customer service teams. Managing WISMO calls can also be very costly because these inquiries consume considerable resources.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Tackling WISMO: Strategic Approaches</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Communicate expected delivery dates <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">at checkout</strong></span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Send <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">proactive emails</strong> when orders leave warehouses</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Deploy <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">event-triggered messages</strong> for delays and complications</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Provide <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">branded tracking pages</strong> enabling real-time order monitoring</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div></section>
    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
